whyP1: 'App Store information is scattered across multiple websites, regions, and tools. Price differences between regions can be significant but hard to discover. IAP details are buried in long product pages. High-resolution icons require manual URL manipulation. Wolffy brings these workflows into one fast, privacy-respecting interface.',
